            "name": "Sheriff's Blessing",
            "sort": 800000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 3
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> Ausken has a physical body</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Ausken touches a willing character and infuses their mind and spirit with bravery. Until the next sunset, the touched character gains a +1 status bonus to all saving throws against fear effects, and any time the character gains the frightened condition, reduce its value by 1. Ausken is always willing and eager to give his blessing to a PC when asked.</p>\n<p><strong>Rank 2</strong> The blessed character now treats any success on a saving throw against a fear effect as a critical success instead.</p>\n<p><strong>Rank 3</strong> Ausken can touch two willing characters to give both of them his blessing, and the effects of the blessing now last for 24 hours.</p>"
                },
